{"type":"text","timestamp":1775876493242,"sessionID":"ses_285850964ffey2ZpSGUQcIATeP","part":{"id":"prt_d7a7ca9130014l0YTDxGWpVrlN","messageID":"msg_d7a7c8638001pYz1wuLeiFIMkT","sessionID":"ses_285850964ffey2ZpSGUQcIATeP","type":"text","text":"## AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider Summary\n\n### **Completed**\n\n**Core Provider Implementations:**\n- **KubernetesProvider** (364 lines providers/, 280 lines services/)\n  - Standard Kubernetes Deployment + NodePort Service\n  - Namespace management, name sanitization\n  - Deployment readiness polling with timeout\n  - Agent status and deletion operations\n  \n- **AgentCubeProvider** (333 lines providers/, 197 lines services/)\n  - AgentRuntime Custom Resource deployment\n  - CRD: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n  - Idempotent CR creation/update\n  - Environment variable support for required URLs\n\n**Provider Architecture:**\n- Base provider interface with `DeploymentResult`/`AgentStatus` dataclasses\n- Custom exception hierarchy (`ProviderError`, `ProviderTimeoutError`, etc.)\n- Retry mechanism with exponential backoff\n- Provider factory pattern for dynamic provider creation\n- Configuration validation and YAML-based persistence\n- Status/event monitoring with polling\n- Plugin system for extensibility\n\n**Testing & Documentation:**\n- 5 unit test files (554 lines) for base components\n- CLI integration with `--provider` flag (k8s/agentcube)\n- IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md with full architecture documentation\n- README updates with provider options\n\n### **Deferred**\n\n**Testing:**\n- Comprehensive unit tests for provider implementations (`test_k8s_provider.py`, `test_agentcube_provider.py`)\n- Integration tests for publish/status workflows\n- Edge case testing (long names, special characters, timeout boundaries)\n- Security testing (sensitive data redaction, RBAC enforcement)\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- RBAC manifests for both providers\n- Provider comparison documentation\n\n**Documentation:**\n- CHANGE.md completion with implementation details\n- Final verification and cleanup\n- Backward compatibility verification","time":{"start":1775876493239,"end":1775876493239}}}
